---
title: Italian Pork Sausage & Veggie Bolognese with Spaghetti & Parmesan
description: Put on your magician's hat and try this simple trick to get the kids eating more veggies... Make a tasty pork sausage bolognese and add grated carrot and baby spinach leaves, letting them cook down until they're barely noticeable. Another trick? Use the back of a spoon to help squeeze the pork out of the sausage casings.
